Navigate Chap to the end of the maze.
Collect treasures to open the door to the exit.
Collect coloured keys to open coloured doors.
Avoid bugs! Making contact with a bug will cause you to lose the game.

Controls:
In Game:
ARROW KEYS - Move Chap
SPACEBAR - Pause game
ESCAPE - Close pause menu
CTRL+S - Save & Exit (your save game will load the next time you launch the game)
CTRL+X - Exit without saving
CTRL+1 - Start game from level 1

In Replay:
UP ARROW - Speed up replay
DOWN ARROW - Slow down replay
SPACEBAR - Toggle auto replay (auto replay is running by default)
RIGHT ARROW - Step through replay (if auto replay isn't running)